<lyrics>[V1]
 Ory sady mitomany
 Aho, ry Jesosy ô,
 Fa tsaroako izany
 Vesatry ny heloko ;
 Koa mba todihonao,
 Raiso ho mpianatrao,
 Ny fanahiko sitrano,
 Atsanganonao ka tano !</lyrics>
<title>Ory sady mitomany FFPM402</title>
</song>